entries.femaleVariant: Thought you could blackmail me, bitch?! Set conditions?!
entries.maleVariant: Thought you could blackmail me, fucker?! Set conditions?!

entries.femaleVariant: Don't know him.
That guy? Never seen him before.
I told you! I fucking told you! I'm not the mole! Jesus Christ!
Shut him up.
Got backup.
Yep. Just little ol' me.
It's the truth.
Talk, dammit!
[Shake hand] Correct.
Got an offer for ya.
That'd be me.
C'mon! I want an answer!
I'll ask again – did that cocksucker sell you any intel?
Come on!
I asked if you came alone!
Christ, Meredith...
All set.
[Shake hand] Got a proposition for you.
You want info, I want a bot. Let's make a deal.
[Take credchip] We got a deal, then.
Sounds solid enough. I'm in.
Try to fuck me in any way, and I'll be seeing you real soon.
You're making a mistake!
Unhand me now before I-- ungh!
You have a plan how to deal with 'em?
Now listen close. This piece of shit, Anthony Gilchrist, is he your contact? Is he the one who leaked intel on the convoy?
Yep. All by my lonesome.
Got any more for me?!
Shut your trap!
I know you spiked the chip.
That the kind of subtlety they teach at Militech? Chip's spiked with a virus, clearly.
That is true.
Meredith Stout. Take it you were the one to call…
That fucking thing ready?
Now answer my questions. Honestly. Forthrightly. Are you here alone?
This bind you're in, I get it.
I'll tell you who's alone. You.
Not another word!
Checks out.
Her you can let go – wanna hear what she has to say.
entries.maleVariant: Him you can let go – wanna hear what he has to say.

entries.femaleVariant: I need a bot – Flathead model.
Hmm... Fine, the latter. But on one condition – you pay with our money.
I got no ties to Militech.
Lemme go!
Get your fuckin' hands off me!
I just wanna talk!
Calm the fuck down! I just wanna talk!
This cunt's already good as dead!
And she'll take you down with her!
Look lively.
Nuh-uh. Know what, Stout? My offer just came off the table.
Mistake, big mistake.
No way, not happenin'.
Got guardian angels. With .50 caliber snipes aimed at your skull.
She's lying.
Try that again and it's two million volts, got it?
Got no ties to Militech. None.
Checks out.
I can help with your mole problem.
Never met anybody named Gilchrist. That the poor fucker right there?
It's true. Doesn't know him.
Y'know, I could help patch the gaps in your convoy security. Prevent a repeat of this fiasco.
Nope. Not interested. Let's hear your offer. I don't have all day.
Your convoy security's a mess. I can help.
All right. Eddies on the credchip are clean.
You don't let me go, your dogs'll have to glue you back together.
Fail to recover that transport, and you're done. With not a soul willin' to help.
So how the fuck do you know so much?
C'mon, all corps use the same playbook. I know the game inside out.
That said, I've jumped a few convoys in my day. Know all the usual suspects. Bet I can help find your mole.
But what I know now won't get you anywhere in that respect.
Somethin' goes wrong, I'm the one they'll fill full of holes, not you. Time you were straight with me. What's on there?
A tracing algorithm, latches onto financial streams. Nothing you need to worry your head about.
You pay with that chip, and that's all you gotta worry about.
Could just take it by force. But they're expecting payment, so... I could go that route, too.
entries.maleVariant: Could just take it by force. But they're expecting payment, so I could go that route, too.

entries.femaleVariant: Listen, I know where the transport is. I can help you. Just want a favor in return.
Hmm...
Guys who ripped you off have it. Promise me that bot, I'll point the finger.
[Take credchip] Fine. Deal.
Nah. Deal's off.
Stout, you bitch, you're done! You're fucking done!
You and everyone under your thumb! Hear that, fellas?!
Do a sweep. Now.
Lemme go.
Jesus, woman, calm down and release me.
You answer me, bitch! Anthony Gilchrist!
Couldn’ta talked normally from the start?
Couldn'ta been chill from the start?
Shut the fuck up. Tell me what you want.
